OL,3,CMan admits to concealing women's body
OL,4,Cbut denies murder
OL,6,FA man has admitted concealing the body
OL,7,Fof a woman but denied murdering her
OL,8,Fand killing five guinea pigs.
OL,10,FGeorge Gordon is accused of killing
OL,11,FDelia McInerney, whose body was
OL,12,Freportedly discovered in the freezer
OL,13,Fof a flat in St Helens, Merseyside, in
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FOn Friday May 1, Gordon appeared by
OL,17,Fvideolink from prison at Liverpool
OL,18,FCrown Court and pleaded not guilty to
OL,19,Fcausing unnecessary suffering to
OL,20,Fprotected animals by killing five
OL,21,Fguinea pigs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
