OL,3,CMan admits to concealing women's body
OL,4,Cbut denies murder
OL,6,FIt can now be reported that Gordon
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty at an earlier hearing
OL,8,Fto preventing a lawful and decent
OL,9,Fburial of a dead body and obstructing
OL,10,Fa coroner by concealing a body between
OL,11,FApril 2023 and January 2026.
OL,13,FHe also admitted three counts of fraud
OL,14,Fby false representation and theft,
OL,15,Fwhich are said to relate to Ms
OL,16,FMcInerney.
OL,18,FGordon, of Gerards Court, St Helens,
OL,19,Fdenied murder at the earlier hearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
