OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777644667
OL,3,CMan admits to concealing women's body
OL,4,Cbut denies murder
OL,6,FMs McInerney, who would have been 64
OL,7,Fat the time her body was discovered,
OL,8,Fwas from Anfield, Liverpool.
OL,10,FIn a tribute released after her death,
OL,11,Fher sister Rita McInerney said: "A
OL,12,Fgreat artist, a free spirit, really
OL,13,F'out there'.
OL,15,F"A rebel. Intelligent with a dynamic
OL,16,Fpersonality. Kind, caring and helpful."
OL,18,FGordon is due to stand trial on
OL,19,FOctober 12.
